                          "<p><strong>EXPLORE</strong></p>",
                          "<p><em>Teacher Moves: Problem Solving Environment</em></p>",
                          "<p>PROVIDING FOR INDIVIDUAL NEEDS</p>",
                          "<p>After giving students some time to try a few ideas, you might suggest that students just begin by comparing two recipes rather than all four at once. </p>",
                          "<p><strong>Suggested questions</strong></p>",
