                          "<p>MAKING THE MATHEMATICS EXPLICIT</p>",
                          "<p>Guide students’ thinking by asking them to think of other ways to set up the relationship. Help make explicit how the strategies for answering the questions are connected and how the proportions can be notated.</p>",
