          "content": {
            "type": "Text",
            "format": "html",
            "text": [
              "<p><strong>a.  </strong>6.5 miles:  using a proportion, 0.25/1 = x/26.  The scale factor is 26.</p><p><strong>b.  </strong>20 miles; using a proportion 0.25/1 = 5/x.  The scale factor is 20. </p>"
            ]
          }
