          "content": {
            "type": "Text",
            "format": "html",
            "text": [
              "<p><em>Elliot</em></p><p>If I buy 40 of the 2-packs of erasers, the total cost will be </p><p>40 × 0.12 = 4.8 = $4.80</p><p>That is more expensive than spending $2.82 for a 40 pack of erasers. The 40-pack is the better deal.</p>"
            ]
          }
