              "<p><strong>a.  </strong>Alicia, Brandon, and Serena wanted to solve the proportion x/4.24 = 6.82/2.2.  Which of the students used a correct method?</p><p><strong>b.  </strong>Of the correct methods, which makes the most sense to you?  Explain your choice.</p>"
