              "<p><em>Example Student Strategies and Reasoning</em></p><p>(Problem Solving Environment)</p><p><em>Strategy 1: Reasoning with Pictures and Estimation</em></p><p>Some students will use the pictures to reason about the quantities. They often discuss how the pizza is shared without doing exact numerical calculations.</p>"
