              "<p><strong>Opening Activity</strong></p><p>Take the questionnaire to estimate how much water is used in your home every day. <a href=\"https://water.usgs.gov/edu/activity-percapita.html\">How much water do you use at home? </a> </p><p><a href=\"https://water.usgs.gov/edu/activity-percapita.html\"></a>Explore your waterway. <a href=\"https://water.usgs.gov/edu/activity-percapita.html\"></a> <a href=\"https://mywaterway.epa.gov/community\">How&#x27;s my waterway? </a> Add your town name or zip code to the search box. </p><p>Then answer the question in the text box below. </p>"
