              "<p><strong>Today&#x27;s Class: Idea Generation (Part 2)</strong></p><p>In today&#x27;s lesson you will continue generating ideas for design solutions, trying to generate more diverse ideas for water conservation design solutions (compared to the ideas you came up with in the last lesson). </p><p>Remember that the purpose of idea generation activities is to help you come up with new ideas for design solutions. You don&#x27;t have to draw well. You don&#x27;t have to like all your ideas. The important thing is to think of new ideas and sketch them. </p>"
